title: Dakine Frankie Pack 26L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Frankie Pack 26L in Juno.
Frankie Pack 26L Features: 
- Side access fleece lined padded laptop compartment
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Fleece lined padded iPad sleeve
- Breathable DriMesh back panel and shoulder straps
- Adjustable sternum strap
- Back panel security pocket
- Top fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Water bottle pocket
- Padded bottom panel
